<h1>CA Brisbane Forum</h1>
<p>Welcome to the Brisbane Coder Academy Forum</p>
<%# this calls the @questions(home_controller.rb) variable for Questions.all(question.rb)
it then gives the @question a variable of question
this variable of an instance variable is used below to loop over this div
in one section the question.gravatar calls the method of gravatar(question.rb)
using the MD5 encryption it produces a random gravatar of a robot(this is inbuilt with gravatar!)
question.email calls upon the pgadmin(online db) and cycles through all the rows and produces the email
as if I was calling upon an array %>
<% for question in @questions %> 
<%# media from bootstrap %>
<div class="media">
    <div class="media-left media-middle">
        <a href="#">
        <img class="media-object" src="<%= question.gravatar %>" >
        </a>
    </div>
    <div class="media-body">
        <h4 class="media-heading"><%= question.email %></h4>
        <%= time_ago_in_words(question.created_at) %>
        <%= question.body %>
    <div>
        <a href="<%= question_path(question) %>" class="btn btn-success btn-xs">View Answers</a>
    </div>    
</div>
<% end %>
